&quot;$LRCX, earnings led to a gap down but it reversed higher, closing with a very beautiful bullish engulfing candle. Indicators show an extended upward breakout trend, breaking the &#39;flag&#39; pattern and reclaiming the moving average support. This setup is suitable not only for intraday trading but also for a swing trade.
For a Friday &#39;lotto&#39; play, watch for a low open and a pullback to 145.8-147. As long as it does not break below 144.8, &#39;roll&#39; into the 150 lottos; they are very cheap. Intraday targets are 149.1, 151.3, the previous high of 153.7, and even 159.
For those who like swing trades, if it holds firmly above 147, you can consider the November 155-160 (Calls).&quot;

